Suggests: smartmontools, nvme-cli
Description: Battery health, firmware updates and diagnostics for ThinkPads
 Lapcare gives ThinkPad owners hardware information, battery health and
 wear analysis, firmware updates via fwupd/LVFS, storage health, one-click
 diagnostics, and exportable diagnostic reports in one native
 GTK4/libadwaita window.
 .
 Lapcare wraps the hardware tooling Linux already has (fwupd, UPower,
 smartctl, sysfs) rather than reimplementing it; every feature degrades
 gracefully when a tool is missing or the hardware is unsupported.
